                  <P>UCB will hold a bidders day on Wednesday 14 June for interested parties to find out more about the development. The event will take place at 3:00 p.m. at UCB and attendees are limited to two per organisation. Please register your interest ahead of the event at 31727.UCBPhase2@macegroup.com.</P>
               </INFO_ADD>
